    "description": "Living in a mage tower near small castle with your teacher one day you wake up and see castle attacked by skeletons! Old mage and castle people will not be able to solve big and truly evil force that tries to invade it, but your hidden genius and uncontrollable curiosity was always waiting for a true big start in your life.<br><br><br><strong>CATCH DIFFERENT SKELETONS</strong><br>Catch skeletons by opening portal from your living room to the castle battlefield. You will be able to catch bigger ones when waves will start getting more hostile.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334920/extras/29c068e1567a4dd2d79dacb73706f476.poster.avif?t=1681558777\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334920/extras/29c068e1567a4dd2d79dacb73706f476.webm?t=1681558777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334920/extras/29c068e1567a4dd2d79dacb73706f476.mp4?t=1681558777\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>DISCOVER A MINE UNDER THE TOWER</strong><br>Manage your skeletons to mine different ore in underground mines and Discover different parts of tunnels to gain access to more rare ore.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334920/extras/fea4a31f3e0230134f3845de9667c079.poster.avif?t=1681558777\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334920/extras/fea4a31f3e0230134f3845de9667c079.webm?t=1681558777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334920/extras/fea4a31f3e0230134f3845de9667c079.mp4?t=1681558777\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>CREATE DIFFERENT MINING EQUIPMENT</strong><br>Create different things using alchemist table to help your skeletons to make them faster and stronger. Stronger skeletons will be able to clear paths to other parts of the mine<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334920/extras/4cfdbd524fe5b88af33f5ac96ea2586b.poster.avif?t=1681558777\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334920/extras/4cfdbd524fe5b88af33f5ac96ea2586b.webm?t=1681558777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334920/extras/4cfdbd524fe5b88af33f5ac96ea2586b.mp4?t=1681558777\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>MANAGE NEIGHBOOR CASTLE</strong><br>Manage transmuted golden coins to help citizens to repair the castle and build better defenses. Which will lead to stronger enemy waves with stronger skeletons.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334920/extras/67f96b5a86284b6ae022c92d1308d67b.poster.avif?t=1681558777\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334920/extras/67f96b5a86284b6ae022c92d1308d67b.webm?t=1681558777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334920/extras/67f96b5a86284b6ae022c92d1308d67b.mp4?t=1681558777\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>DISCOVER UNKNOWN SPELLS</strong><br>Discover new spells by pronouncing them with your voice on rune table. Use spells to enchant skeletons equipment to help them mine really strong ore.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334920/extras/93ccad7b3986e75c8c10202f78fb8daf.poster.avif?t=1681558777\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334920/extras/93ccad7b3986e75c8c10202f78fb8daf.webm?t=1681558777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334920/extras/93ccad7b3986e75c8c10202f78fb8daf.mp4?t=1681558777\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
